    - rid: 107151359355650172
      type: {class: WeighedChoice, ns: , asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        modules:
        - weight: 45
          module:
          - rid: 107151359355650173
          output: 'What is better than having a talented painter under our sway?
            Having that same artist dedicate his skills to slandering our primary
            rival!

            [Gained 40 Zeal]

'
        - weight: 45
          module:
          - rid: 107151359355650174
          output: 'The artist is horrified by our attempt at slander. It seems we
            have caused him to become disillusioned with all sects. It could have
            been worse; at least now he shall not paint for anyone!

            [Lost
            10 Bliss]

'
        - weight: 10
          module:
          - rid: 107151359355650175
          output: "What a tragedy! It appears our rivals had the very same idea.
            The painter found himself at the center of the worst aspects of our warring
            folds. Such was the chaos that the youth eventually lost his faith\u2014and
            with it, his will to live. Today, the city loses a rising star.\r\n[Lost
            55 Zeal]\r\n"
